parameters.name: SECONDS
parameters.description:
Spacecraft Time (elapsed seconds from epoch 
                       2001-01-01T00:00:00.000 UTC). Derived from spacecraft 
                       clock time.

parameters.name: FRACT
parameters.description:
Spacecraft Time (fractional seconds in units of 1/100 second).
                       Derived from spacecraft clock time.
